data.description: Beautiful Estate in the heart of Arlington, spacious floor plan with an updated kitchen. Hardwood upstairs was newly replaced (3 months ago). Minutes away from Arlington Elementary-Middle-High school and many Shopping-Entertainment essentials. Comes with a plus sized Den upstairs that can be used as an office. Backyard is one of the biggest in the neighborhood and comes with a covered patio for summer fun nights with the family. This house has HOME written all over it!
